{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "驼子将小方引荐给商队中的\"箭组\"。箭组头领唐麟矮小精干，全身充满可怕力量，不多话却极有威严。小方初入箭组即遭蒙藏勇士马沙摔跤试探，轻松将马沙摔倒；又遭果尔洛族战士加答持刀暗袭，小方夺刀反制后却以勇士之礼释放加答。加答以藏人最高礼节哈达相赠，二人结为朋友。驼子告知箭组负责护卫贵重货物，可疑者可杀无赦。小方暗自怀疑这批货物可能就是被盗的三十万两黄金，而箭组成员可能就是猫盗。黄昏时小方与加答当值巡逻，加答告知挚友马沙在沙漠中失踪后再无音讯。返回巡逻点时发现马沙的尸体——这位摔跤好手竟被人以摔跤手法扼杀。更可怕的是，他们随即发现了第二个暴死者，死亡阴影笼罩了整个队伍。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他姓方。”“我想用他。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他有用？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_sha",
      "speaker_name": "马沙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我来试试他有多大本事。”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_sha",
      "speaker_name": "马沙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好小子，果然有两手。”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你再试试这一刀。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你要杀我，我就该杀你，你杀不死我，就该死在我手里。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "text": "“这样子是不是很公平？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“公平！”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我不能杀你，因为你是个勇士，不怕死的勇士。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们这一组的代号是'箭'，现在你已是'箭组'的人，也得像别人一样，每天轮班一次，我们这一次带回去的货物很贵重，只要有可疑的人想来动我们的货物，你就可以杀了他。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你甚至可以用刚才加答要杀你的方法杀了他！”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“今天你是在黄昏时当班，我派加答跟你一班，到时他会去跟你连络。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“现在你可以去照顾你的女人了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那个女人看起来是个好女人，这里的女人太少，男人太多，你要特别小心。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这个姓方的武功很不错。”“你知不知道他的武功来历？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不知道！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你有没有问过他？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“没有。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lin",
      "speaker_name": "唐麟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“为什么不问？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“因为……”",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_jia_da",
      "text": "“我看得出马沙也是个勇士，他是不是你的朋友？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是的。”“但是我以后恐怕永远看不见他了。”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“太阳还在天正中的时候，他要我陪他去放粪，我没有粪，我没有去，他去了。”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jia_da",
      "speaker_name": "加答",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他去了后就没有回来过。”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    }
  ],
